'''奥索'''（{{lang-is|Össur hf.}}）是一家冰岛医疗器械公司，主要生产[[義肢|義肢]]和矫形器材。

==历史==
1971年在[[冰岛|冰岛]][[雷克雅未克|雷克雅未克]]成立，1999年在[[冰岛证券交易所|冰岛证券交易所]]挂牌上市。2009年在[[哥本哈根证券交易所|哥本哈根证券交易所]]挂牌上市。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Össur Celebrates 20 Years as a Publicly Traded Company|url=https://www.nasdaq.com/press-release/ossur-celebrates-20-years-as-a-publicly-traded-company-2019-12-17|access-date=2020-09-23|website=www.nasdaq.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210717155657/https://www.nasdaq.com/press-release/ossur-celebrates-20-years-as-a-publicly-traded-company-2019-12-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[https://annual-report.ossur.com/download/files/Ossur_AnnualReport_2019.pdf Annual Report.] {{Wayback|url=https://annual-report.ossur.com/download/files/Ossur_AnnualReport_2019.pdf |date=20210717154429 }}，年报。</ref>2006年9月成立中国办事处。

==荣誉==
2006年被[[世界经济论坛|世界经济论坛]]评为“科技先驱”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.weforum.org/sessions/summary/new-edge-technology|title=The New Edge of Technology|publisher=[[World_Economic_Forum|World Economic Forum]]|access-date=2021-07-17|archive-date=2014-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129074209/http://www.weforum.org/sessions/summary/new-edge-technology|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=SFC Michael McNaughton|url=https://supportourwarheroes.net/index.php/meet-our-heroes/16-sfc-michael-mcnaughton|access-date=2020-09-23|website=supportourwarheroes.net|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104215820/https://supportourwarheroes.net/index.php/meet-our-heroes/16-sfc-michael-mcnaughton|dead-url=no}}</ref>

